#

Chinese Black Pepper Beef Stir-Fry

25 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

Chinese

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

Stir-FryQuick MealBeefChinese Cuisine

Description

A quick and delicious stir-fry featuring tender beef in a spicy black pepper sauce, perfect for a weeknight dinner!

Ingredients

  • beef sirloin: 1 pound
  • bell pepper: 1 (sliced)
  • onion: 1 (sliced)
  • garlic: 3 cloves (minced)
  • soy sauce: 3 tablespoons
  • black pepper: 2 teaspoons
  • cornstarch: 1 tablespoon
  • vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
  • green onions: 2 (sliced for garnish)
